<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home | Sunlit Flavours</title>

    <!-- Google Fonts -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lavishly+Yours&family=Libre+Baskerville:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&family=Montserrat:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <!-- Font Awesome -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.6.0/css/all.min.css">

    <!-- Bootstrap -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

    <!-- Other Bootstrap for Footer -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet">
    

    <!-- Custom CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Including the header partial / Navbar-->
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section id="hero" class="hero">
        <div class="container text-center">
            <h1>Welcome to <span class="title" style="text-decoration-color: white;"><%= restaurantName %></span></h1>
            <p class="tagline">Revel In Unforgettable Feasts!</p>
            <a href="/menu" class="btn btn-light"><i class="fa-solid fa-utensils"></i> Explore Menu</a>
            <a href="/order" class="btn btn-success"><i class="fa-solid fa-cart-shopping"></i> Order Now</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Menu Highlights Section -->
    <section id="menu-highlights" class="menu-highlights">
        <h2 class="section_heading">Our Best Bites</h2>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <% menuItems.forEach(item => { %>
                    <div class="col-md">
                        <div class="card mb-4">
                            <img src="<%= item.imageUrl %>" class="card-img-top" alt="<%= item.name %>">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h5 class="card-title"><%= item.name %></h5>
                                <p class="card-text"><%= item.description %></p>
                                <p class="card-text"><strong>Price: ₹<%= item.price %></strong></p>
                                <button class="btn btn-success add-to-cart w-100" data-id="<%= item._id %>" data-name="<%= item.name %>" data-price="<%= item.price %>" data-image="<%= item.imageUrl %>">
                                  <i class="fas fa-cart-plus"></i> Order
                              </button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                <% }); %>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Testimonials Section -->
    <section id="testimonials" class="testimonials secondary_bg">
      <h2 class="section_heading">Raving Reviews</h2>
      <div class="slideshow-container container">
        <div class="mySlides">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md">
              <img class="testimonials-img" src="/images/testimonials-woman1.jpg" alt="Dixie Normous">
            </div>
            <div class="col-md testimonies">
              <q>None of the places I’ve tried really fill me up like this one does. Big, bold flavors that leave you coming back for more, again and again. It’s the perfect combination of satisfying and unforgettable.</q>
              <p class="author">&#8212 Dixie Normous</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mySlides">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md">
              <img class="testimonials-img" src="/images/testimonials-man1.jpg" alt="Ben Dover">
            </div>
            <div class="col-md">
              <q>This place really knows how to take care of business. I came in empty and left completely satisfied—like the perfect mix of juicy buns bent over, ready for the sausage, topped off with those smooth milkshakes to finish it right.</q>
              <p class="author">&#8212 Ben Dover</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mySlides">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md">
              <img class="testimonials-img" src="/images/testimonials-woman2.jpg" alt="Lotta Cox">
            </div>
            <div class="col-md">
              <q>The portions here are huge, just how I like it—satisfying and filling. I left completely stuffed and craving for more. Trust me, this place knows how to pack it in!</q>
              <p class="author">&#8212 Lotta Cox</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mySlides">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md">
              <img class="testimonials-img" src="/images/testimonials-couple.jpg" alt="Hugh-Jass">
            </div>
            <div class="col-md">
              <q>We thought we could handle it, but the moment we sat down, we were both blown away. The portions were huge, hot, and packed tight—just the way we like it. By the time we were done, we were both stuffed, begging for one last course to finish it off. And let’s just say, the dessert was the perfect, sweet finale to a night we’ll never forget.</q>
              <p class="author">&#8212 Hugh-Jass</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <a class="prev" onclick="plusSlides(-1)">&#10094;</a>
        <a class="next" onclick="plusSlides(1)">&#10095;</a>
      </div>

      <div class="dot-container">
        <span class="dot" onclick="currentSlide(1)"></span>
        <span class="dot" onclick="currentSlide(2)"></span>
        <span class="dot" onclick="currentSlide(3)"></span>
        <span class="dot" onclick="currentSlide(4)"></span>
      </div>

      <script>
        var slideIndex = 1;
        var slideTimer; // To manage the auto-slide interval

        showSlides(slideIndex);
        startAutoSlide(); // Start the auto-slide initially

        function plusSlides(n) {
          clearTimeout(slideTimer); // Stop the auto-slide temporarily
          showSlides(slideIndex += n);
          startAutoSlide(); // Restart the auto-slide after a manual change
        }

        function currentSlide(n) {
          clearTimeout(slideTimer); // Stop the auto-slide temporarily
          showSlides(slideIndex = n);
          startAutoSlide(); // Restart the auto-slide after a manual change
        }

        function showSlides(n) {
          var i;
          var slides = document.getElementsByClassName("mySlides");
          var dots = document.getElementsByClassName("dot");

          if (n > slides.length) { slideIndex = 1 }
          if (n < 1) { slideIndex = slides.length }
  
          for (i = 0; i < slides.length; i++) {
            slides[i].style.display = "none";
          }
          for (i = 0; i < dots.length; i++) {
            dots[i].className = dots[i].className.replace(" active", "");
          }

          slides[slideIndex - 1].style.display = "block";
          dots[slideIndex - 1].className += " active";
        }

        function startAutoSlide() {
          slideTimer = setTimeout(function() {
          plusSlides(1);
          }, 5000); // Change slide every 5 seconds
        }
      </script>
    </section>

    <!-- Contact Section -->
    <section id="contact" class="contact">
      <div class="container">
          <h2 class="section_heading">Drop Us a Line</h2>
          <p>We'd love to hear from you! Reach out to us and we'll get back to you as soon as possible.</p>
          
          <div class="contact_details row">
              <div class="contact_info col-md">
                  <h3><i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot"></i> Visit Us</h3>
                  <p>123 SunCity Ave, Rajasthan, India</p>
              </div>
              <div class="contact_info col-md">
                  <h3><i class="fa-solid fa-phone"></i> Call Us</h3>
                  <p>+123 456 7890</p>
              </div>
              <div class="contact_info col-md">
                  <h3><i class="fa-solid fa-envelope"></i> Email Us</h3>
                  <p><a href="mailto:contact@sunlitflavours.com">contact@sunlitflavours.com</a></p>
              </div>
          </div>
  
          <form class="contact_form" action="/contact" method="post">
              <div class="form_group">
                  <label for="name">Your Name</label>
                  <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Enter your name" required>
              </div>
              <div class="form_group">
                  <label for="email">Your Email</label>
                  <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="Enter your email" required>
              </div>
              <div class="form_group">
                  <label for="message">Your Message</label>
                  <textarea id="message" name="message" placeholder="Enter your message" required></textarea>
              </div>
              <button type="submit" class="submit_btn btn-success"><i class="fa-solid fa-paper-plane"></i> Send Message</button>
          </form>
      </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Footer Partial -->
  <%- include('partials/footer') %>

    <!-- Custom JS for add to cart functionality -->
     <script src="js/menu.js"></script> 

    <!-- Bootstrap JS, and jQuery -->
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.5.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
